This strategy is specifically designed for H1 and H4 swing trading, using a structured trend-following approach.

It combines:
EMA 50 & EMA 200 → Primary trend filter
Market Structure (HH/HL & LH/LL) → Directional confirmation
RSI → Momentum and overbought/oversold filter
ATR → Volatility-based dynamic Stop Loss
Minimum Risk:Reward 1:2
Optional Break Even and ATR Trailing Stop

The strategy focuses on entering retracements within a strong trend rather than chasing breakouts.
